      <title>欧洲央行：欧元区银行降低抵押贷款门槛但需求持续下降</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euro-zone-banks-lower-bar-mortgages-demand-keeps-falling-ecb-2024-04-09/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行周二的一项调查显示，上季度欧元区银行两年多来首次降低了抵押贷款审批门槛，但由于借贷成本高企和经济停滞，信贷需求持续下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/euro-zone-banks-lower-bar-mortgages-demand-keeps-falling-ecb-2024-04-09/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Apr 2024 08:02:18 GMT</pubDate>
